verse.lines:
You ask why I am happy
so I’ll just tell you why,
Because my sins are gone;

‘Twas at the old time altar where God came in my heart
And now,
my sins are gone;

When Satan comes to tempt me and tries to make me doubt,
I say,
my sins are gone;

I’m living now for Jesus,
I’m happy night and day,
Because my sins are gone;
